Yocto layer for configuring a Linux distro on a Raspberry Pi 4.

To be used together with
- https://github.com/agherzan/meta-raspberrypi
- https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded
- https://git.yoctoproject.org/git/poky

Instructions on how to use available here:
https://www.hackster.io/david-gherghita/air-quality-monitor-using-raspberry-pi-4-sps30-and-azure-03cb42
